title: Tarot Book Collection
description:
This is a torrent of my tarot e-book collection that I have amassed as of September 2013. Will be updated in the future as I keep collecting. 

Books included:

*21 Ways to Read a Tarot Card - Mary K. Greer
*Complete Book of Tarot Reversals - Mary K. Greer
*Understanding the Tarot Court - Mary K. Greer & Tom Little
*Seventy-Eight Degrees of Wisdom - Rachel Pollack
*Tarot & Magic - Donald Michael Kraig
*Past Life and Karmic Tarot - Edain McCoy
*Great Symbols of Tarot - A. E. Waite
*The Pictorial Key to the Tarot - A. E. Waite
*Qabalistic Tarot - Robert Wang
*Enochian Tarot Handbook - Scheuler
*How to Perform a Psychic Reading, A Beginner's Guide to Reading Tarot Cards - James Gregory
*Insight Tarot - Dawn Rothwell
*Mastering the Tarot - Paul Fenton Smith
*The Symbolism of the Tarot - P. D. Ouspensky
*Introduction to the Study of the Tarot - Paul Foster Case
*Oracle of the Tarot, A Course on Tarot Divination - Paul Foster Case
*The SEcret Doctrine of the Tarot - Paul F. Case
*Tarot Get the Whole Story - James Ricklef
*Tarot Outside the Box - Valerie Sim
*Tarot Shadow Work - Christine Jette
*Tarot Spells - Janina Renee
*Tarot Tips - Amberstone
*The Book of Tarot - S. G. Estes
*The New Golden Dawn Ritual Tarot - Cicero
*The Tarot - S. L. MacGregor Mathers
*The Tarot of the Bohemians - Papus
*The Wisdom of Tarot - Elisabeth Haich
*Ultimately Tarot - John Field
*The Initiatic Path in the Arcane of Tarot and Kabbalah - Samael Aun Weor
*Tarot History Timeline - Dame Gabby
*The Continental Tarots - Christine Payne Towler
*Sex Magic, Tantra, and Tarot - Christopher Hyatt
*Evercoming Son in the Light of the Tarot - Frater Achad
*Greer Cinnabar Tarot Course
*Learning the Tarot (In 19 Lessons)
*Min's Complete Tarot Manual & Tarot Pak
*The Ultimate Encyclopedia of Fortune Telling - Michael Johnstone
